merge("fff", 6, ...) → "fff":6 (len=3)
put("c", 3) → "c":3 (len=1)
put("aa", 1) → Replaces "dd" (len=2) with "aa":1 (same length).
put("bb", 2) → Replaces "aa" with "bb":2 (same length).
merge("e", 5, ...) → Updates "c" (len=1) to 3 + 5 = 8.
Final Entries:
"c":8 (len=1)
"bb":2 (len=2)
"fff":6 (len=3)
Output Order: Sorted by length → c:8 bb:2 fff:6.
